title: HOUR 3- Matt Entz Aug 28, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Matt Entz Aug 28, 2020
description:
Dan and crew break down the biggest story lines as the NFL season approaches--such as which rookie quarterbacks will have the most success as well as the possibility of a one-game player strike to raise social justice awareness. Also, North Dakota State head football coach Matt Entz joins the program.
